name: SST-02_4 ALGORITHM
description: v4W.ENko - "SST-02_4 ALGORITHM" is the next serial name of "SUBSTRATE STONE TOWER" algorithm which is developed to continet this abstraction. The Towers are generated with natural stone patterns along algorithm of "substrate". The camera is flying around the towers elliptically. Tops of the towers are grown from the cells of "substrate" with 3d extrusion with random seed 11. Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 90frames.
